X-Temp technology is designed to adapt to your temperature and activity to keep you cool and dry for all day comfort. FreshIQ advanc edodor protection technology attacks the odor-causing bacteria in your clothing that causes your t-shirts to smell – so now you can feel fresh all day. Three-button placket with dyed-to-match buttons. All the comfort of Hanes with our famous tag-fre e neckline. Machine wash cold with like colors non chlorine bleach when needed tumble dry medium.
